'''''Boetie Gaan Border Toe''''' ni filime yo gusebanya 1984 yashyizweho mugihe cy'intambara y'umupaka wa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>Boetie Gaan Border Toe | The Observation Post <nowiki>https://samilhistory.com</nowiki> › tag › boetie-gaan-border-toe</ref> . Iyi filime yayobowe na Regardt van den Bergh, ikaba ikinamo Arnold Vosloo, Frank Dankert na Frank Opperman . Umusaruro wafashijwe n’ingabo z’Afurika yepfo (SADF)<ref>Boetie Goes To The Border (1984) — The Movie Database (TMDB) (themoviedb.org)</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Boetie van Tonder, umusore wo muri Afrikaner, ashobora kwinjizwa mu gisirikare cya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>Boetie Gaan Border Toe Movie - Filmoria <nowiki>https://www.filmoria.co.uk</nowiki> › movie-list › boetie-gaan-b...</ref>. Nubwo mu mizo ya mbere yiyemeje kurwanya umurimo w’igihugu no kwanga amabwiriza, ahita abona ihumure ari kumwe n’abasirikare bagenzi be mu gihe bahuye n’imyitozo ikaze y’amahugurwa y’ibanze ndetse no koherezwa ku mupaka wa [[Angola|Angola.]]<ref>Boetie Gaan Border Toe! - Welcome | Gender and War since ... <nowiki>https://gwonline.unc.edu</nowiki> › node</ref> 

